data.eml:eml: A new fossil lacewing genus from the Middle Jurassic of Inner Mongolia, China (Neuroptera: Osmylidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Wang, Yongjie, Liu, Zhiqi, Ren, Dong (2009): A new fossil lacewing genus from the Middle Jurassic of Inner Mongolia, China (Neuroptera: Osmylidae). Zootaxa 2034: 65-68, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.186346
